title: Uranium Backup v9.2.2.5920
description:
Uranium Backup v9.2.2.5920

The most complete backup software, appreciated by tens of thousands of users across the world.
Discover USilio, the IT Management Console!

Uranium is a light and reliable backup software for the protection of your personal and business data. It supports Usilio, the IT Management Console, that allows to organize the clients, monitor and run the backup sets, receive automated reports and integrates Supremo.

Uranium Backup is powerful but its interface keeps the things simple. You can schedule a backup in no time. A reporting system will alert you in case of failure. Everything is under your control.

Virtual machine backup
Uranium Backup is an easy-to-use and flexible software to perform hot backups of Hyper-V and VMware ESX/ESXi/vSphere virtual machines.

Exchange / SQL backup
Uranium can perform hot backups of MySQL, MariaDB, Microsoft SQL Server databases and Exchange servers.

Drive Image Backup
Uranium can create backup images of your system disks that can be restored in case of disaster (bare metal restore).

Tape backup
Uranium is a powerful solution for tape backups. It supports any type of tape drive (DAT, LTO, etc..) on any Windows system.

Official Website: http://www.uranium-backup.com/
